2017-04-21 20-00-00:
	Title: Release 20170421 out now!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: Almost to the day half a year after our last stable release, we are proud to finally present to you our latest work - OpenRA Release 20170421!\n\nWith a huge number of new maps and balance changes, fixes for annoying multiplayer bugs and HiDPI support, this release should have something for everyone.\n\nCheck out the full news post at http://openra.net, have a look at http://changelog.openra.net for the complete changelog, and grab an installer for your OS from http://openra.net/download!\n\nWe hope you'll enjoy this newest release from OpenRA. Thanks for playing!
